%% GH Copilot code - starts
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UserRegistrationComponent
    participant RegistrationFormComponent
    participant FormValidationService
    participant ApiService
    participant NotificationService
    participant RegistrationSuccessComponent
    participant RegistrationErrorComponent

    User->>UserRegistrationComponent: Initiates registration
    UserRegistrationComponent->>RegistrationFormComponent: Display registration form
    User->>RegistrationFormComponent: Enter registration details
    RegistrationFormComponent->>FormValidationService: Validate form inputs
    FormValidationService-->>RegistrationFormComponent: Return validation result
    alt Valid inputs
        RegistrationFormComponent->>UserRegistrationComponent: Submit registration data
        UserRegistrationComponent->>UserRegistrationService: Register user
        UserRegistrationService->>ApiService: Send registration request
        ApiService-->>UserRegistrationService: Return success response
        UserRegistrationService-->>UserRegistrationComponent: Return registration result
        UserRegistrationComponent->>NotificationService: Show success notification
        NotificationService-->>User: Display success message
        UserRegistrationComponent->>RegistrationSuccessComponent: Show success UI
    else Invalid inputs
        FormValidationService-->>RegistrationFormComponent: Return error(s)
        RegistrationFormComponent->>NotificationService: Show error notification
        NotificationService-->>User: Display error message
        RegistrationFormComponent->>RegistrationErrorComponent: Show error UI
    end
%% GH Copilot code - end
